    """Select a tip key from TIPS, optionally biased by self.tip_weights.

    If tip_weights is None, falls back to a uniform draw via self.rng.choice().
    Otherwise, nonpositive/missing weights are treated as 0.0, and the tip
    is chosen via self.rng.random() against the cumulative distribution.
    If all weights are zero/invalid, falls back to a uniform draw.
    """
